plg_mootit is a tool to integrate the Moot.it forums into the
Joomla 3.0 environment.

REQUIRES:      Joomla 3.x
               Moot.it Account available free at http://moot.it/
           
INSTALLATION:  Use the Joomla Package Manager to install this plugin.


